    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to reach its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip. The chassis remains composed with a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and aluminum subframes. Crucially, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and ARP bolts, and the throttle actuators have been upgraded to address common failure points in the S65\u2019s valvetrain and induction system. It delivers a raw, linear torque curve and an unmatched induction note.",
