      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with only minor road nicks consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you'll find a pristine, non-smoking cabin where the seats remain supportive and the carpets are free of stains. Every feature, from the power sunroof to the premium audio system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, backed by a consistent service history. We recently completed a multi-point inspection, fresh oil change, and tire rotation to ensure it is road-trip ready. This car offers a quiet, composed ride and represents an excellent value for someone seeking reliability without the new-car price tag.",
